Entries.SourceString: Level Up and spend Battle Stars to claim rewards in the order you want!

Text.SourceString: Unspent Battle Stars exchanged for rewards at season end.
Spend Battle Stars to claim Battle Pass rewards in the order you want!
Pick up Alien Artifacts across the Island or inside Cosmic Chests .
Earn 5 Battle Stars every time you level up.
Spend Alien Artifacts to claim styles for the customizable Kymera outfit.
Complete quests from Characters or Pay Phones to earn Bars that persist between matches.
Spend Bars to upgrade your weapons with upgrade benches, grab items from vending machines, and a lot more.
